data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Discover an exceptional investment opportunity in Palmetto, FL! This 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom property offers nearly 1000 sqft of potential and countless possibilities for investors. Nestled in a neighborhood on the cusp of transformation, this property's strategic location provides access to a range of local attractions, nearby communities, parks, and recreational options. With a generous lot size, a convenient wrap-around driveway, and a carport, this property presents a canvas for expansion and enhancement. This investor special beckons those with vision and a professional touch to unlock its full potential and capitalize on the thriving real estate market in the area. Reach out today to seize this prime investment opportunity and join the transformation of this dynamic community.
